可由一些常用的layer构成一个简单","link":"/posts/ai_system%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0","cover":"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2025/01/18/289087756/12edfcc1b1caa1c38f32d65ad931b4e8_6695806414558017006.png?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,png","date":"2025-05-01T15:00:00-07:10"},{"title":"CMU CSAPP bomblab phase1 ~ phase5 解答","tags":[],"categories":["technology"],"author":"","excerpt":"# 写在前面\n\n贴一个下载链接[CS:APP3e, Bryant and O'Hallaron (cmu.edu)](https://csapp.cs.cmu.edu/3e/labs.html)，点击","link":"/posts/bomblab","cover":"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2025/04/06/289087756/d11618345d3ab4448a716e918e811079_4619182930752436350.jpg?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,jpg","date":"2025-01-20"},{"title":"daemon 与 服务","tags":[],"categories":["technology"],"author":"","excerpt":"\r\n> 本文内容有待完善。 \r\n\r\n- daemon，字面上意思为“守护神、恶魔”，通常没有 GUI 界面，是 Unix/Linux 环境的典型产物。具体表现为后台运行、不与终端交互的单个进程，是一种","link":"/posts/daemon","cover":"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2024/07/13/225492857/af8f2b802a4e7b6b1b9ecb1201f7f11c_2216729078109522029.png?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,png","date":"2025-02-20"},{"title":"docker与dev container插件的使用","tags":[],"categories":["technology"],"author":"","excerpt":"\n> 本文侧重1.讲解docker的插件使用。2.视觉consimulation项目的跨环境迁移\n# 基础配置\n- 安装vscode。\n- 在vscode安装 Docker 插件与ms-vscode-","link":"/posts/docker","cover":"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2025/04/06/289087756/8352c80eb95793ada1c5ad84c776e01c_3760274156792306482.png?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,png","date":"2025-01-20"},{"title":"NLP Review","tags":[],"categories":["NLP"],"author":"","excerpt":"\r\n## 词法分析\r\n### 英文分词\r\n定义规则，单词还原，去掉过去式单复数等等，一般步骤是：\r\n- 查词典， 如果词典中有该词， 直接确定该词的原形；\r\n- 根据不同情况查找相应规则对单词进行还原","link":"/posts/nlp","cover":"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2025/07/15/161972981/be2f928a59cab05c5801447ee24b8b90_6126